  Intake[intake received]
  Normalize[project normalized]
  Research[requirements gathered]
  Review[review decision captured]
  Seal[submission package sealed]
  Submit[submission attempted]
  Status[external status ingested]
  Resolve[comments resolved / resubmission]
  Approve[approval recorded]
  Audit[audit and evidence retrieval]

  Intake --> Normalize --> Research --> Review --> Seal --> Submit --> Status
